fabric.ast

Interface FabricExtFactory

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractFabExtFactory_c, FabricFabExtFactory_c, FabricJifExtFactory_c

    public interface FabricExtFactory
    Factory for extensions for all of the AST nodes in the Fabric language. Note that the created extensions need not be FabricExts.
